        "content": "## ‚è∞ Automatic Trigger\n\n**Runs twice daily:**\n- 9:00 AM\n- 9:00 PM\n\nTimezone: America/Santiago (Chile)\n\nYou can modify these times or add more trigger hours in the Schedule Trigger configuration."
